{"tid":1485996,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【延續李蛇教路】唔完美、可接受、但亦要改善。","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:52:33.000Z","uid":88420,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"787577341af23867047db7cf2e39bd364dda2c2c","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家仲記唔記得李蛇？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日警察記者會，教左我地一句話！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1465819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1465819</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟係機場打鬼當晚<br />\n引用左狗狗<span style=\"color: red;\">李桂華</span>，回應賊贓嫁禍時間嘅一句<br />\n用作解釋如何理解社運同路人之間嘅意見分歧。<br />\n係度要多謝連登巴絲嘅捧場，好多留言都讚果個 post 正面，有建設性。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日大家都辛苦啦！<br />\n正正係咁，我想大家記翻起，李蛇送俾我地嘅一句話</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dA8zjFH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdA8zjFH.png&h=42d4893b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔完美、可接受、但亦都要改善</span></span><br />\n<br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n下面，係小弟針對今日嘅小小分析<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地未贏，但係贏嘅機會依然好大。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAtLrg3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAtLrg3.png&h=98b59b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Source: Associated Press 美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n今日 170 萬人破紀錄參與集會，落曬大雨，但係大家依然繼續耐心等候，係國際傳媒嘅鏡頭下，<span style=\"color: violet;\">我地贏得好好</span>。<br />\n<br />\n不過當民陣宣布集會結束嘅時候，仍然有好多手足聚集係夏愨道。連登巴絲用盡九牛二虎之力，現場兄弟姊妹<span style=\"color: red;\">叫極都係唔走</span>，大家開始擔心，<span style=\"color: violet;\">我地會唔會好似五年前咁輸</span>？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地唔會輸，只要記住李蛇呢句話，我地會贏！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haovCry.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaovCry.png&h=10549880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔完美</span></span><br />\n<br />\n回顧今日嘅行動，其實有好多<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔完美</span>嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n唔單止係金鐘，其實民陣疏散嘅安排亦都係<span style=\"color: violet;\">唔完美</span>！<br />\n<br />\n最近呢幾次大型示威，乖乖地排入維園嘅人，永遠都行得最辛苦。<br />\n天后炮台山中途加入嘅人潮，往往擋住維園出高士威道嘅出口，令到維園準時撚離開嘅速度極低。<br />\n今日落大雨，<span style=\"color: violet;\">入維園排隊嘅人全部濕曬，由頭濕到落底褲果隻</span>。<br />\n民陣其實可以安排更多糾察，定時截住天后出發嘅朋友，俾維園嘅朋友更快可以離開。最理想嘅，係俾維園嘅人離開曬，再 escort 天后朋友入維園等。<br />\n<br />\n民陣嘅大台，一味叫大家「加油」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽到我都好燥，你可唔可以強硬小小，「立即要求」警方開路，而唔係「懇請」警方「5-10分鐘後」回應交代是否「考慮」開路？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣嘅安排，小弟認為係唔完美</span>。<br />\n<br />\n至於夜晚金鐘，大家就咁坐起度，乜都唔做。<br />\n雖然有好多人叫身邊人返屋企，涼冷氣，<br />\n即使後來有防暴狗狗係附近增援，但係依然有好多人係度磨下磨下。<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，<span style=\"color: gold;\">做任何行動，都要有目標</span>。<br />\n今晚留係金鐘，唔叫口號，到底有咩目標？假如無目標，不如早小小休息，補充體力！<br />\n<br />\n所以，<span style=\"color: gold;\">今晚金鐘突然賴死唔走，係唔完美架</span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可接受</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係，但係，今日嘅所有唔完美<br />\n係絕對絕對絕對<span style=\"color: gold;\">「可接受」</span>！<br />\n<br />\n關於民陣集會疏散安排，絕對可接受！<br />\n狗狗係兩日前，先發出反對通知書。<br />\n或者佢地係有不足之處，但係喺咁<span style=\"color: violet;\">短時間內要處理咁多事情，執行有不足之處，可以接受</span>。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，金鐘手足們決定留守，我都<span style=\"color: gold;\">絕對絕對理解</span>、絕對<span style=\"color: gold;\">絕對可以接受</span>！<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月以來，手足係金鐘流過多少眼淚？為香港未來灑下了多少血汗？大家見到夏愨道，想留守，想守護自己爭取返黎嘅成果，係可以理解嘅。<br />\n<br />\n呢種講法雖然好似好膠，但係夏愨道作為一個具有共同代表性嘅地方 (place)，無形中承載著大家抗爭過程中嘅回憶，有承接、有感情。<br />\n<br />\n我地出得黎行，出黎勇武，就係要為左香港好。<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">為香港好，係因為我地對呢片土地有感情，有回憶。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，留守、留戀、死守、戀戰，係可接受架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但亦需要改善</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQjOpoV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQjOpoV.png&h=b94457ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得呢位手足？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非、勇武，已經無需要再分一條界線。</span><br />\n<br />\n和理非，勇武，是一種選擇。<br />\n但係喺大時代裡，<span style=\"color: gold;\">進步、改善，係必需要的</span>。<br />\n<br />\n下次，假如係和理非場合，去到目的地影張相，打完卡，就翻屋企涼冷氣啦。<br />\n<br />\n見到疑似鬼嘅，唔駛打佢地，同佢地影幅相，感謝他們支持「平反六四」、支持「五大訴求」，好似幾位靚仔巴打咁！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繼續行，就會贏！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n六月十二日，我地係金鐘食第一次催淚煙。<br />\n我地都無估到，2019 年，香港人可以行到咁遠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aWV6baO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaWV6baO.jpg&h=4dbb04f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不分化、不割𥱊，最後係要提醒身邊同路人，<br />\n我地一直要進步、學習、適應，<br />\n同呢個可惡卑鄙嘅港共政權、中央政府抗爭落去！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Stand with Hong Kong, Fight for Freedom</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7c677ffbd52a3eec7773372b505a895216eb37","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:39:20.000Z","msg":"自推 10 次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520834d5b631847e223eafc0784e973df126ad99","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea85a720e1c84798f1358ed8ff4fd2391d6ec89","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa16399b70e26d5ef3f7a47c65d30f46ce71fbee","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:40:41.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67301ed4a8c27da2d275939998b0430b1edd1a3f","tid":1485996,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:40:42.000Z","msg":"［永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進］今日總結，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制，請大家對手足保持體諒嘅態度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485890</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日總結，我認為大家要互相體諒，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制<br />\n<br />\n例如之前呢三個鐘已經去到金鐘同散咗場嘅巴打，因為擔心前線安危，加上今日目標已經達成（搶佔國際輿論），冇必要死守，所以叫走，但始終人已經唔係身處現場，冇上帝視角，望住live 仲見到咁多人，自然開始心急，語氣上亦變得可能唔係太好<br />\n<br />\n同時之間，前線亦想所有人平平安安走曬，自己最後一批先走，咁當然一定會有鬼從中叫人留低/ 賴死唔走，迫你留低「保護」佢哋，同樣前線亦冇上帝視角，難以判斷係手足定係鬼，加上客觀因素（現場人多電話收到嘅信號會少/ 局勢變化可能太快）散嘅速度自然亦會慢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係呢一句：<br />\n永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，請大家對手足保持體諒嘅態度，兵荒馬亂之際大家嘅心情難免心急，語氣上亦會有所失儀，唯希望大家之後仍然可以再度團結，齊上齊落，打贏呢一場逆權運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcc1d7e4be58a4088fa78b00bbdf7fdd271f48f","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:41:09.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c73b712720dc3b6fc478902c7fe50367ac09bff","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"自推 6/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182915bc3f56b3af78b702d5eabbbe8b8389dfe3","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:41:47.000Z","msg":"自推 7/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b119c73339853838801ffb9702c30b854f5ff9f4","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:42:02.000Z","msg":"自推 8/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6baa927aa3cde76266afb6127e7488491fdfa71","tid":1485996,"uid":55231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c09b97f61e0420392a17f019c3357bee9b72192b","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:42:15.000Z","msg":"自推 9/10 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a93cae8dd90a2d8a04097fd4a81915c2cc4a5a","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:42:48.000Z","msg":"自推 10/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71788e7db1fda7750083518e21e015df9216181f","tid":1485996,"uid":2248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c042daea31c988979376dfc78ad515192a836f4b","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd72d0c04b1141afcee0bfaedd8469721c26cf30","tid":1485996,"uid":122122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dc4d96096dd3663b12466b227455aafacff57d","tid":1485996,"uid":64273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ad4b9dabe7df19b92e5c66767114bc084e47559","tid":1485996,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b613b20ab12eec15f720d75fbf535a938932adbe","tid":1485996,"uid":66276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}